t(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2019/02/betty/embed/#?secret=ODMZF3NP2h\" data-secret=\"ODMZF3NP2h\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tout d‚Äôabord, un grand bravo √† la douzaine de fran√ßais ayant contribu√© √† cette nouvelle version de notre CMS !</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cette nouvelle version majeure de WordPress contient exactement <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;type=defect+(bug)&amp;milestone=5.1&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">303</a> corrections, <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;type=enhancement&amp;milestone=5.1&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=type&amp;col=owner&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">156</a> am√©liorations, <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;type=feature+request&amp;milestone=5.1&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=type&amp;col=owner&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">9</a> demandes de nouvelles fonctionnalit√©s, et <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;type=task+(blessed)&amp;milestone=5.1&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=type&amp;col=owner&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">23</a> autres t√¢ches <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;milestone=5.1&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">marqu√©es comme r√©solues dans WordPress 5.1</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Voici un article r√©capitulant ces changements. Chacun d&rsquo;entre eux est accompagn√© des ressources correspondantes 